      'Nilekani, N. (2018). Imagining India: The Idea of a Renewed Nation. Penguin.',
      'Infosys. (2024). Infosys Annual Report 2023-24. BSE Filing.',
      'Sen, S. (2022). Infosys: The Journey. Business Standard.',
      'HBS. (2019). Infosys: The Global Delivery Model. Harvard Business School Case Study.',
